{"article_id":"wXMWmB7WA50KlEVa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Paul Manafort ' s legal team faces a critical choice","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"as he heads to trial :","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"how aggressively the former Trump campaign chairman should base his defense on alleged political bias and misconduct by federal investigators .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Manafort , a criminal defendant","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"fighting two separate cases ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"is uniquely positioned","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to try to dredge up information on bias or potential overreach by FBI and Justice Department officials","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"who have played roles in special counsel Robert Mueller ' s probe of ties between the Trump campaign and Russia .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Whether Manafort will seek to uncover and spotlight disparaging details about federal officials ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"potentially including an FBI agent","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"dismissed from Mueller ' s team last year ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"has become the subject of speculation and anticipation by lawyers","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"involved in the Russia investigation .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" This is something","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"we ' ve all been talking about , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"said one defense attorney","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"representing a witness in Mueller ' s probe .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" It ' s a hard question . \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Some expect Manafort to take a slash-and-burn approach .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"they ' re going to try to throw any dirt possible , \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"said former federal prosecutor Randall Eliason .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"\" If he ' s going to trial ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"then I would expect it to be an all-out war ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and I wouldn ' t be surprised","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"if they try to make those kinds of claims","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that the prosecution is tainted . \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Sign up today","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"An aggressive claim of bias by Manafort is unlikely to derail the prosecution","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that now threatens him with the prospect","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"of spending the rest of his life behind bars .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"It would also bring some risk :","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Lawyers warn","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that it could anger the judges","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"presiding over his cases ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"who might see the strategy as a frivolous diversion","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that could drag the trials into a political morass .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"But such moves could also draw public attention to alleged abuses by federal investigators ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"whom some congressional Republicans have accused of a brazen anti-Trump vendetta .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"That might draw the attention and sympathy of President Donald Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"from whom Manafort may be hoping to win a pardon .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" The degree","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"to which he can show broader FBI misconduct in his investigation","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"can lay a foundation for a pardon , \"","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"said George Washington University law professor Jonathan Turley .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"\" Thus far , Manafort has not been able to benefit from the controversy","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"surrounding the FBI .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"To the extent he can make himself part of that narrative ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"it can only help him","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"- certainly with the president . \"","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"Manafort is facing numerous charges","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"related to his political work for pro-Russian politicians in Ukraine ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"including money laundering , bank fraud , tax evasion and failing to disclose","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that he was lobbying for a foreign power .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Democrats also suspect","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"that Manafort may have been a key intermediary between the 2016 Trump campaign and Kremlin agents .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"With deadlines looming for pretrial motions ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"many lawyers say","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that for Manafort , the risk","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"of raising the misconduct issue in court","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"is well worth taking .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" I don ' t see a particular downside ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"other than angering the judge , \"","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"said Solomon Wisenberg , a defense attorney and former deputy independent counsel in the Whitewater investigation","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who noted","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that Manafort ' s team has already irritated one presiding judge .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Manafort ' s defense could allege outrageous government conduct ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"but such motions rarely prevail .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Demands for details on any malfeasance by investigators and attorneys","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"who have worked on the case","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"might stand a better chance ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"lawyers say .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Prosecutors have told the federal judges","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"overseeing the pair of cases against Manafort","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that they are nearly finished turning over relevant information about his alleged crimes .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"That process would typically include documents , witness statements , FBI reports and more .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Prosecutors are obliged to give defense attorneys any evidence","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that tends to show a defendant ' s innocence","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"- so-called exculpatory evidence -","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"or otherwise bolster his defense ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"including information","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"undercutting the credibility of government witnesses .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"However , those basic principles leave room for disagreement","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"- including over how prosecutors should handle derogatory information about an investigator","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"removed from the case for alleged bias or malfeasance","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"but who will not take the witness stand .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"That could describe FBI agent Peter Strzok ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"whom Mueller removed from his team last summer over texts","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"he exchanged with an FBI lawyer in 2016","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"that were harshly critical of Trump .","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"Strzok had a senior role in the Russia investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"although it is not clear how involved he was in Manafort ' s case .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Judges often reject defense discovery requests","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"related to suspected misconduct ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"but Turley said","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"the Mueller probe is unusual","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"given that \" there are already matters in the public record","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"raising concerns about political bias and influence . \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"\" Having said that ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"judges tend to be leery of opening this door","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"because they ' re never sure","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"when they can shut it , \"","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"The 332 people","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"connected to the Russia probes","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"A analysis reveals","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"that the investigations into the 2016 election and its aftermath now involve hundreds of people in Washington , Moscow and around the world .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Lawyers say","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"there ' s no bright-line rule","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"about what information the defense is entitled to in such circumstances .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"\" If","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"[ Strzok ] were a witness ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that would definitely be discoverable .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"If he ' s not a witness ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"it ' s not as clear cut ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"but it may still be discoverable , \"","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"said one defense attorney","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"closely tracking the case .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"when it comes to Strzok and other federal officials","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"connected to the Russia probe ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"Manafort faces an obstacle :","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"While the charges","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"he currently faces","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"are the product of Mueller ' s Russia investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"they are not related to Trump or the 2016 campaign .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"His political work for Ukraine and the payments","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"he took","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"long predated his work for Trump .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"\" If an investigator was insubordinate three years ago in an unrelated matter ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that doesn ' t have much pertinence to the investigator ' s work in a current case , \"","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"said Jeff Welty , a professor of government and public law at the University of North Carolina .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"\" Ultimately , it isn ' t enough that an investigator has done something improper at some point in his or her life","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"- it needs to be sufficiently significant","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that is it ' material ' to the current investigation . \"","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Manafort ' s defense team declined to comment for this story ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"citing a judicial gag order .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Manafort ' s lawyers already have an ample public record","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"from which to draw ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"including the work of multiple congressional Russia investigations as well as a Justice Department Office of Inspector General probe into pre-election investigative actions at the FBI and DOJ .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"A report","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"detailing Inspector General Michael Horowitz ' s findings","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"may emerge soon .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Some evidence","depth":17},{"id":152,"text":"Horowitz gathered ,","depth":17},{"id":153,"text":"such as text messages","depth":17},{"id":154,"text":"involving Strzok ,","depth":17},{"id":155,"text":"has been turned over to Congress ,","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"but much more is still awaiting review at the Justice Department and FBI .","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"Trump has complained publicly","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"that the pace of the disclosures is too slow .","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"Both the Justice Department and Mueller ' s office declined to comment for this story .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"Even after the OIG report is released ,","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"Manafort ' s legal team could try to demand fuller detail , such as witness interviews .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"This dynamic is one reason","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"inspector general inquiries are typically delayed","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"until the related criminal cases are over ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"but Horowitz ' s probe of pre-election bias seems to have become at least partially entangled in Mueller ' s work .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"Past inspector general reviews have prompted prosecutors to make disclosures","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"aiding defendants .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"One 1997 report exposed deficiencies at the FBI laboratory","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"that included ethical questions about lab examiners .","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"The Justice Department reviewed the examiners ' work","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"and notified defendants about potentially relevant findings .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"Another inspector general report in 2014 said","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"the department should have done even more in that case","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"to make \" appropriate and timely disclosures to affected defendants . \"","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"FBI personnel","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"criticized in the forthcoming IG report","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"appear to have been involved in search and surveillance applications during the Russia investigation and possibly also witness interviews .","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"For example , Strzok is among the FBI agents","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"who interviewed then-national security adviser Michael Flynn in January 2017 .","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"( Flynn later pleaded guilty to lying to federal investigators . )","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"Strzok also appears to have been involved in preparing Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act applications","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"related to the Russia probe .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"Whether any of those relate directly to Manafort is unclear ,","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"although the FBI placed one of Manafort ' s associates , Russian-Ukrainian national Konstantin Kilimnik , under court-ordered surveillance .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"Defendants in FISA cases often seek the underlying applications ,","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"though none are known to have persuaded a judge to turn them over .","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"But Trump 's February decision","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"to release a House GOP memo","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"offering details on the FISA applications against ex-Trump campaign adviser Carter Page","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"may have partially declassified those applications .","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"At the moment , Manafort is the only defendant in a case","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"Mueller has brought","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"who is contesting the charges .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"The rest have either entered guilty pleas","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"or are Russian businesses or Russian nationals","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"believed to be overseas .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"However , Flynn ' s supporters and family members have urged him to seek to reverse his guilty plea","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"by arguing","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"that new revelations of alleged FBI misconduct were unknown to him last December .","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"Even though Flynn already admitted guilt ,","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"Judge Emmet Sullivan ordered prosecutors to provide Flynn with all exculpatory evidence","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"that could mitigate his punishment .","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"Such discovery orders","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"following a guilty plea","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"are uncommon ,","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"but Sullivan is a stickler on the issue","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"after overseeing the corruption trial of the late Sen. Ted Stevens","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"( R-Alaska ) .","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"His conviction was vacated","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"after prosecutors withheld evidence","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"that could have aided the defense .","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"For now , though , there ' s no sign","depth":9},{"id":213,"text":"Flynn plans to try to force prosecutors to fork over more information","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"than they ' ve given up .","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"His attorney , Robert Kelner , declined to comment .","depth":8},{"id":216,"text":"So far , Manafort ' s defense team has filed just one discovery motion :","depth":8},{"id":217,"text":"asking","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"that prosecutors cough up unredacted copies of affidavits","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"used","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"to obtain search warrants last year ,","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"including ones for Manafort ' s Alexandria , Virginia , condo and a storage locker .","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"Manafort ' s lawyers , Kevin Downing and Thomas Zehnle , filed a motion Friday night","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"asking that evidence","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"taken from the locker","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"be suppressed .","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"Eliason said","depth":7},{"id":227,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"while the defense could persuade a judge to require more disclosure about bias or misconduct by investigators ,","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"introducing those issues at trial would be difficult .","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"\" Even if you can make the case","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"that several years ago there was misconduct by one agent","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"involved ,","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"it would be hard to raise","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"unless you can show","depth":9},{"id":235,"text":"they manufactured evidence","depth":10},{"id":236,"text":"or made up facts","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"you got into in your trial , \"","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"Eliason added .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":477,"left":265,"right":476,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":241,"right":264,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":240,"right":2,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":245,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":242,"right":244,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":242,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":5,"right":243,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":254,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":249,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":247,"right":248,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":8,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":252,"right":17,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":250,"right":251,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":18,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":256,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":255,"right":21,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":257,"right":259,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":259,"left":24,"right":258,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":476,"left":348,"right":475,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":348,"left":273,"right":347,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":267,"right":272,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":27,"right":266,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":266,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":30,"right":271,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":269,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":268,"right":33,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":347,"left":300,"right":346,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":294,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":275,"right":293,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":36,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":37,"right":38,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":39,"right":292,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":279,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":40,"right":278,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":276,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":282,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":280,"right":281,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":285,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":284,"right":52,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":51,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":286,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":55,"right":287,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":297,"right":298,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":295,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":346,"left":315,"right":345,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":309,"right":314,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":304,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":301,"right":303,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":301,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":303,"left":302,"right":68,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"